          <title>
            <string language="en">Andersonville: Prisoner of War Camp</string>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Andersonville: Kriegsgefangen-Lager</string>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">Andersonville : Camp de prisonnier de 
guerre</string>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">Andersonville: Acampamento do prisioneiro de
guerra</string>
            <string language="x-mt-it">Andersonville: Accampamento del prigioniero 
di guerra</string>
            <string language="x-mt-el">Andersonville: Στρατόπεδο αιχμαλώτων πολέμου</string>
            <string language="x-mt-es">Andersonville: Campo del prisionero de 
guerra</string>
          </title>
          <description>
            <string language="en">examines the conditions of Camp Sumter (in Andersonville, Georgia), the largest and most notorious of prisoner of war camps during the Civil War.</string>
          </description>
          <keyword>
            <string language="en">Social Sciences</string>
          </keyword>
          <language>en</language>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-de">überprüft die Zustände des Lagers Sumter (in 
Andersonville, in Georgia), das größte und das am notorischsten von 
den Kriegsgefangenlagern während des Bürgerkrieges.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">examine les conditions du camp Sumter (en 
Andersonville, Géorgie), le plus grand et le plus notoire des camps 
de prisonnier de guerre pendant la guerre civile.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">examina as condições do acampamento Sumter (em 
Andersonville, em Geórgia), o maior e mais notorious de acampamentos 
do prisioneiro de guerra durante a guerra civil.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-it">esamina gli stati dell'accampamento Sumter (in 
Andersonville, in Georgia), il più grande e più rinomato degli 
accampamenti del prigioniero di guerra durante la guerra civile.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-el">εξετάζει τους όρους του στρατόπεδου Sumter (σε 
Andersonville, τη Γεωργία), ο μεγαλύτερος και ο πιό πασίγνωστος
των στρατόπεδων αιχμαλώτων πολέμου κατά τη διάρκεια του εμφύλιου
πολέμου.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-es">examina las condiciones del campo Sumter (en 
Andersonville, Georgia), el el más grande y más notorio de campos 
del prisionero de guerra durante la guerra civil.</string>
          </description>
          <keyword>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Sozialwissenschaften</string>
          </keyword>
          <keyword>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">Les Sciences Sociales</string>
          </keyword>
          <keyword>
